# 🔍 7. Practical Examples

## 🌐 HTTP Enumeration

```bash
nmap -p 80 --script http-enum target.com
```

## 🔐 Check SSL Info

```bash
nmap --script ssl-cert -p 443 target.com
```

## 🧪 Vulnerability Scan

```bash
nmap --script vuln target.com
```

---

# ⚡ 8. Advanced Script Usage

## 🎛️ Script Arguments (`--script-args`)

Customize script behavior:

```bash
nmap --script http-brute --script-args userdb=users.txt,passdb=pass.txt target.com
```

## 🔍 Multiple Scripts

```bash
nmap --script "http-*,ssl-*" target.com
```

## ⏱️ Combine with Timing

```bash
nmap -T4 --script vuln target.com
```

