# 🧬 9. Writing Your Own NSE Script (Beginner → Advanced)

## 🧱 Basic Script Structure

```lua
description = [[
Simple example script
]]

author = "Your Name"
license = "Same as Nmap"
categories = {"discovery"}

portrule = function(host, port)
  return port.open
end

action = function(host, port)
  return "Port is open!"
end
```

---

## 🧠 Key Components

### 🔹 `portrule` / `hostrule`

* Defines when script runs

### 🔹 `action`

* Main logic

---

## 📚 Using Libraries

Example with HTTP:

```lua
local http = require "http"

action = function(host, port)
  local response = http.get(host, port, "/")
  return response.status
end
```

